{"tid":1014827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拆穿偽科學】負離子係無。撚。用。㗎","createTime":"2019-02-09T13:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T06:41:17.000Z","uid":138409,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"daa3f94f362e2bf41c18617b7d6adb132fb6d1eb","tid":1014827,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZQ--scjcAZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZQ--scjcAZ4&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=194f5635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZQ--scjcAZ4</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">tl;dr<br />\n</span></span><br />\n基本上支持負離子好處嘅研究<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">研究方法上大部分都有問題</span>，例如sample size 太細、又或者未能排除係安慰劑效應<br />\n而且由於空氣中負離子高嘅地方，正好係大自然中如瀑布/海灘等地區<br />\n負離子表面上對情緒有正面影響，<br />\n好大機會只係因為自然環境本身對情緒有正面影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n有關負離子作用有大量研究，以下係review /meta-analysis<br />\n<br />\nAir ions and mood outcomes: a review and meta-analysis.<br />\nPerez V, Alexander DD, Bailey WH.<br />\nBMC Psychiatry. 2013 Jan 15;13:29.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23320516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpubmed%2F23320516&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=0e90438f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23320516</a><br />\n<br />\nAir ions and respiratory function outcomes: a comprehensive review<br />\nDominik D Alexander, William H Bailey, Vanessa Perez, Meghan E Mitchell, and Steave Su<br />\nJ Negat Results Biomed. 2013; 12: 14.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3848581/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3848581%2F&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=fa248de7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3848581/</a><br />\n<br />\nExposure of laboratory animals to small air ions: a systematic review of biological and behavioral studies.<br />\nBailey WH, Williams AL, Leonhard MJ.<br />\nBiomed Eng Online. 2018 Jun 5; 17(1):72.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29866122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpubmed%2F29866122&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI9xiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=98389d3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29866122</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映<br />\n</span></span><br />\n我真的很無助，可以請你花五分鐘閱讀以下嗎？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cdpseT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cdpseT</a>"},{"pid":"e4ab61a2de4a42d8030a21130bb6d1a596fd63f1","tid":1014827,"uid":163841,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:40:24.000Z","msg":"有冇中文版？"},{"pid":"7d599458a9aa4235b148a5f8979f1bfe8c17139c","tid":1014827,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4ab61a2de4a42d8030a21130bb6d1a596fd63f1","tid":1014827,"uid":163841,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:40:24.000Z","msg":"有冇中文版？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"你嘅意思係條片？sor 無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係基本上條片嘅主要論點已經sum up咗係tl;dr度"},{"pid":"389b09aa98fddff812483289c3a42a8cebc4daf0","tid":1014827,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"一早知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企有個負離子風筒吹咗5,6年唔覺有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc8b8027cce3040ce943786b15961cd90d0ec22","tid":1014827,"u